<!--
вҡ пёҸвҡ пёҸвҡ пёҸ иӯҰе‘ҠпјҡжӯӨжӘ”жЎҲе·Ій…ҚзҪ®еҢ–пјҢи«ӢеӢҝзӣҙжҺҘдҝ®ж”№пјҒвҡ пёҸвҡ пёҸвҡ пёҸ

жӯӨжЁЎзө„е·ІйҒ·з§»еҲ°й…ҚзҪ®еҢ–зі»зөұпјҢжүҖжңүе…§е®№з”ұд»ҘдёӢй…ҚзҪ®жӘ”жҺ§еҲ¶пјҡ
рҹ“Ғ core/configs/report_descriptions.config.js

еҰӮйңҖдҝ®ж”№жӯӨжЁЎзө„зҡ„д»»дҪ•е…§е®№пјҲжЁҷйЎҢгҖҒж¬„дҪҚгҖҒжҢүйҲ•зӯүпјүпјҢ
и«Ӣз·ЁијҜдёҠиҝ°й…ҚзҪ®жӘ”пјҢдҝ®ж”№жӯӨ HTML жӘ”жЎҲе°ҮдёҚжңғз”ҹж•ҲгҖӮ

жӯӨжӘ”жЎҲе·ІйҮҚж–°е‘ҪеҗҚзӮә .html.bakпјҢеғ…дҫӣеҸғиҖғгҖӮ

й…ҚзҪ®еҢ–ж—Ҙжңҹпјҡ2026-02-04
й…ҚзҪ®еҢ–еҺҹеӣ пјҡзөұдёҖзі»зөұжһ¶ж§ӢпјҢжҸҗй«ҳеҸҜз¶ӯиӯ·жҖ§
-->
<div data-module="report_descriptions">
<div class="content-header with-actions">
    <div>
        <h2>еҲ—еҚ°е ұиЎЁиӘӘжҳҺ</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">з®ЎзҗҶеҗ„йЎһеҲ—еҚ°е ұиЎЁзҡ„иӘӘжҳҺж–Үеӯ—</p>
    </div>
    <div class="header-actions">
        <button type="button" class="btn primary" data-action="create">
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> ж–°еўһ
        </button>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content-area">
    <!-- жЁЎзө„иӯҰе‘ҠиЁҠжҒҜеҚҖ -->
    <div class="module-alert hidden" data-report-descriptions-alert></div>

    <!-- зҜ©йҒёе·Ҙе…·еҲ— -->
    <section class="module-toolbar compact">
        <form class="filter-form" data-report-descriptions-filter>
            <div class="form-grid">
                <label>
                    <span>й—ңйҚөеӯ—</span>
                    <input type="text" name="keyword" placeholder="е ұиЎЁд»Јзўј / е ұиЎЁеҗҚзЁұ">
                </label>
                <label>
                    <span>зӢҖж…Ӣ</span>
                    <select name="is_active">
                        <option value="">е…ЁйғЁ</option>
                        <option value="1">е•ҹз”Ё</option>
                        <option value="0">еҒңз”Ё</option>
                    </select>
                </label>
                <label>
                    <span>жҜҸй ҒзӯҶж•ё</span>
                    <select name="perPage">
                        <option value="10">10</option>
                        <option value="20" selected>20</option>
                        <option value="50">50</option>
                    </select>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-actions">
                <button type="submit" class="primary">еҘ—з”Ё</button>
                <button type="button" data-action="reset-filter">йҮҚиЁӯ</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </section>

    <!-- иіҮж–ҷиЎЁж јеҚҖ -->
    <section class="table-section">
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="data-table" data-report-descriptions-table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th data-sort="report_code" data-column="report_code" scope="col">е ұиЎЁд»Јзўј <i class="fas fa-sort"></i></th>
                        <th data-sort="report_name" data-column="report_name" scope="col">е ұиЎЁеҗҚзЁұ <i class="fas fa-sort"></i></th>
                        <th data-column="report_name_en" scope="col">иӢұж–ҮеҗҚзЁұ</th>
                        <th data-column="description" scope="col">иӘӘжҳҺж‘ҳиҰҒ</th>
                        <th data-sort="is_active" data-column="is_active" scope="col">зӢҖж…Ӣ <i class="fas fa-sort"></i></th>
                        <th data-sort="updated_at" data-column="updated_at" scope="col">жӣҙж–°жҷӮй–“ <i class="fas fa-sort"></i></th>
                        <th scope="col">ж“ҚдҪң</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="7" class="text-center">иіҮж–ҷијүе…Ҙдёӯ...</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="pagination" data-report-descriptions-pagination></div>
    </section>
</div>

<!-- ж–°еўһ/з·ЁијҜ Modal -->
<div class="modal-overlay hidden" data-report-descriptions-modal>
    <div class="modal-window large">
        <button type="button" class="modal-close" data-action="close-modal" aria-label="й—ңй–ү">
            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
        </button>
        <h3 data-modal-title>ж–°еўһе ұиЎЁиӘӘжҳҺ</h3>

        <!-- Modal е…§йғЁйҢҜиӘӨиЁҠжҒҜйЎҜзӨәеҚҖ -->
        <div class="modal-alert hidden" data-report-descriptions-modal-alert role="alert"></div>

        <form data-report-descriptions-form novalidate>
            <input type="hidden" name="id">

            <section class="form-section">
                <h4>еҹәжң¬иіҮиЁҠ</h4>
                <div class="form-grid">
                    <label class="inline-label">
                        <span>е ұиЎЁд»Јзўј <abbr title="еҝ…еЎ«">*</abbr></span>
                        <input type="text" name="report_code" required placeholder="дҫӢеҰӮ: screening_inspection" autocomplete="off">
                    </label>
                    <label class="inline-label">
                        <span>жҳҜеҗҰе•ҹз”Ё</span>
                        <select name="is_active">
                            <option value="1">е•ҹз”Ё</option>
                            <option value="0">еҒңз”Ё</option>
                        </select>
                    </label>
                    <label class="inline-label">
                        <span>е ұиЎЁеҗҚзЁұ <abbr title="еҝ…еЎ«">*</abbr></span>
                        <input type="text" name="report_name" required placeholder="дҫӢеҰӮ: зҜ©еҲҶжӘўй©—зөҗжһңе ұиЎЁ" autocomplete="off">
                    </label>
                    <label class="inline-label">
                        <span>е ұиЎЁиӢұж–ҮеҗҚзЁұ</span>
                        <input type="text" name="report_name_en" placeholder="дҫӢеҰӮ: Screening Inspection Report" autocomplete="off">
                    </label>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="form-section">
                <h4>иӘӘжҳҺе…§е®№пјҲдёӯж–Үпјү</h4>
                <div class="form-grid">
                    <label class="inline-label full-width">
                        <span>е ұиЎЁиӘӘжҳҺ</span>
                        <textarea name="description" rows="5" placeholder="и«Ӣијёе…Ҙе ұиЎЁиӘӘжҳҺе…§е®№пјҢе°ҮйЎҜзӨәеңЁеҲ—еҚ°е ұиЎЁдёҠ"></textarea>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="form-section">
                <h4>иӘӘжҳҺе…§е®№пјҲиӢұж–Үпјү</h4>
                <div class="form-grid">
                    <label class="inline-label full-width">
                        <span>Report Description</span>
                        <textarea name="description_en" rows="5" placeholder="Please enter the report description in English"></textarea>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="form-actions align-right">
                <button type="button" class="outline" data-action="cancel">еҸ–ж¶Ҳ</button>
                <button type="submit" class="primary" data-action="save">е„Іеӯҳ</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
